        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for <hi rend="italic">Science and culture</hi> [1881].</p>  
<p>Refers to "Automatism" ["On the hypothesis that animals are automata"], wishing THH could review himself and answer himself and thus go on <hi rend="italic">ad infinitum</hi> to the joy and instruction of the world.</p> 
